                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_108025">Staverton</placeName>.

<persName>
                           <forename>Nicholas</forename>, prior of <orgName role="prior" key="org_108004">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </orgName>
                        </persName>, called to warranty by <persName>
                           <forename>Emma</forename> 
                           <surname>Crok</surname>
                        </persName>, recognizes by a fine made at <placeName key="place_107054">Northampton</placeName> the right of <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> de <surname>Morton</surname>
                        </persName> in a moiety of half a virgate and a messuage in <placeName key="place_108025">Staverton</placeName> held at a rent of 18d. for the prior after an assize of mort d’ancestor had been summoned between them. For this William gave the prior ½ mark. 
